{
  "id": "adv_card_aoi_10_03",
  "title": "井川葵 3話 大切なのは、楽しむこと",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "なるほどな。四人で合わせる時間なんてなかったのに\n最高のパフォーマンスが出来た理由が、よく分かったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. Even though the four of you didn’t have time to rehearse together‚\nI understand now why your performance turned out so great.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_03-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "それは何よりだよ\nじゃあ寮に着いたし、ここでお別れだね。お休み",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s good to hear.\nWell‚ we’re at the dorm. I’ll say goodbye here. Good night.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 15.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あー……待ってくれ、質問が後一つ残ってただろ？\nそっちも気になっててな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah—wait‚ there was still one more question‚ wasn’t there?\nI’ve been curious about that too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 23.1833333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 23.1833333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いや……そもそもあの勝負所で、どうして満足に\n練習も出来ていない、未発表の新曲をやったんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No… first of all‚ at that crucial moment—\nwhy did you perform an unreleased new song you hadn’t even practiced enough?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 32.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 32.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_03-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、そういえばそんな質問もあったね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ right‚ you did ask that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.9666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "あの勝負所で、いきなり新曲をやったことにも\nもしかして深い意味が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You suddenly performed a new song at such a crucial moment—\nwas there some deeper meaning behind that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 44.1000015259
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_03-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "ないよ\nその方が面白いかなって思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nope.\nI just thought it’d be more interesting that way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_03-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "莉央も最初はあっけにとられてたけど\n大笑いして、いいわねって言ってくれたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio was taken aback at first‚\nbut she burst out laughing and said‚ “I like it.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.1043961366,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 53.4000015259
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "えぇっ！？　待て待て待て、葵だけならともかく\n莉央さんまでそんなことを言い出すなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What!? Wait‚ wait‚ wait—if it were just you‚ I’d understand‚\nbut Rio-san too? I can’t believe she said that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 60.1333348592
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_03-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "僕だけならともかくってなんだよ\n酷いなぁ、{user}君は",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you mean‚ “if it were just me”?\nYou’re awful‚ {user}-kun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 65.6000015259
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_03-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、莉央は思うところがあったのかもしれないね\n小難しいことを考えるのが好きだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ maybe Rio had her own thoughts about it.\nShe likes to think deeply about things.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_03-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "「貴方のおかげで楽しむことを思い出したわ」とか\n「私達の新たな出発にふさわしいわ」とかさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She said something like‚ “Thanks to you‚ I remembered how to enjoy it‚”\nor “This is the perfect new beginning for us.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.4100554422,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_03-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "そういうのを言葉にするのは、莉央に任せるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll leave that kind of poetic stuff to Rio.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.6666656494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 81.6666656494
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 85.4666656494
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "葵らしいな。だからこそ、あの日\nあんなパフォーマンスを生み出せたんだろうな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s so like you‚ Aoi. And that’s exactly why\nyou all could create such a performance that day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "それならそうと、もっと早く教えてくれても\n良かったんじゃないか？　ずっと気になってたんだぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But couldn’t you have told me sooner?\nI’ve been wondering about it all this time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 98.2666656494
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_03-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、あえてもったいぶった方が\n{user}君がやきもきして面白いかなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ I thought it would be fun\nwatching {user}-kun get all restless about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_03-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "何度も聞きに来たり、こうして帰りに\n送ってくれたりして、なかなか楽しかったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You kept coming to ask‚ and even\nwalked me home like this. It was actually pretty fun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.2793824307,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――MV撮影当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—The Day of the MV Shoot",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.9666656494,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1266.6651408000007,
          "startTime": 113.2333307902
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.2333307902
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ごめん、前の仕事が押して遅くなった\n葵、撮影の調子はどうだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ the previous job ran late.\nAoi‚ how’s the filming going?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_03-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "遅いよ、{user}君。さっき終わって\n今、映像チェックをしてるところだ。一緒に見ようか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re late‚ {user}-kun. It just finished.\nI’m checking the footage now. Wanna watch it together?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.9333297729
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、分かった。にしても、今回の衣装、格好いいな\n事前に目にはしてたけど、とても良く似合ってるよ、葵",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sure. By the way‚ the outfit this time looks great.\nI’d seen it before‚ but it really suits you‚ Aoi.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 137.3666631062
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_03-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "うん、僕もそう思うよ\nそれに、君に褒められると悪い気はしないね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I think so too.\nAnd hearing that from you doesn’t feel bad at all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 144.6333297729
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_03-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "さぁ、お喋りはこれくらいにして\n映像をチェックしよう。ほら、隣に座って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ enough chatting.\nLet’s check the footage. Come sit next to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "……映像から葵の気合いが伝わってくる。凄くいいな\nまるで、戦いに赴く騎士みたいだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I can feel your passion from the footage. It’s amazing.\nYou look like a knight going into battle.",
