      "text": "『戦い』、か。莉央さんも言ってたが\nまるでLizNoirが歩んできた道のりそのものだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Battle‚” huh. Rio-san mentioned that too.\nIt’s like the very path LizNoir has walked.",
        "id": ""
